<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你今天<delay8 />也會參加捕蟲大會吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />停在花上的昆蟲<delay8 />還有水面上的昆蟲<delay8 />
都很容易被忽略哩。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />路過那附近的時候<delay8 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要記得仔～細觀察喔！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在捕蟲大會中，<delay8 />
似乎是看參賽者<delay8 />能在既定時間內<delay8 />
抓到多少蟲吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一個勁地衝刺，<delay8 />昆蟲會溜走；<delay20 />
但要是太過謹慎，<delay8 />也會消耗時間<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />我決定了！<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然想也想不出個辦法來，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就靠氣勢來應付了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我小時候<delay8 />經常混在男生堆中，<delay8 />
跟著他們一起鬥蟲呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是很強的唷！<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還被冠上個頭銜，<delay40 />叫做<delay8 />
「鍬形蟲訓練家<tag a="110" b="10" />」呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我好像還曾經用紙箱<delay8 />做出鍬形蟲的顎，<delay8 />
然後戴在頭上<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay8 />現在回想起來還真害臊啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說今天<delay8 /><colour id="3" />龍克斯<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
為了捕蟲大會而來到廣場啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來外頭<delay8 />正熱鬧得很呢！<delay20 />
如果你也打算參加的話，
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />要不要去看看啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昆蟲呢，<delay8 />會從花朵上採蜜，<delay20 />
花朵呢，<delay8 />則是請昆蟲運花粉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是所謂的<delay8 />互助合作吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也真想<delay8 />跟死黨<delay8 />
維持這種關係啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>